original: You've picked up a Tank Helmet. The visor on the helmet can be raised or lowered by pressing the Grab key while the helmet is selected in the Pip-Boy, which will allow for masks and glasses to be worn while the visor is up.

original: You've equipped a gas mask, helmet, radiation suit, or similar item that helps block radiation that you breathe in. The condition of these items will degrade while you are standing in irradiated areas, and this penalty will be increased while walking, and further while running.
translation:
你已装备了防毒面具、头盔、防辐射服或类似物品，
%r这些物品有助于阻挡你吸入的辐射。
%r当你在辐射区域站立时，这些物品的耐久会下降，

original: You've equipped a backpack. Backpacks naturally grant substantially increased carry weight, but they also reduce your AP regeneration speed. They often also have stat maluses, which will be reduced as your Survival skill increases.
translation:
你已装备了一个背包。
%r背包自然能显著增加携带重量，
%r但它们也会降低你的行动点数恢复速度。
%r它们通常还有属性减益，
%r这些减益将随着你生存技能的提高而减少。

original: You've equipped an item which can use an enhanced vision mode. These items are charged with Small Energy Cells via your Pip-Boy, which maintains a universal vision-mode charge. The vision modes on these items can be engaged or disengaged by while holding 'grab' and pressing your Pip-Boy control while outside the Pip-Boy.
translation:
你已装备了一个可以使用增强视觉模式的物品。
%r这些物品通过你的Pip-Boy使用小型能量电池充电，以维持通用的视觉模式充电。

original:
Hey there handsome...

My husband won't be back in town until the 25th, so when you're off work, I want you to come in through my... back door again, and put out my fire like you did last week...

You're used to dealing with so much hot air that I'm sure you'll find the key.
translation:
嘿，帅哥...

我丈夫要到25号才回城，所以等你下班的时候，
我想你再从...后门进来，像上周一样扑灭我的欲火...

你习惯了应对那么多热空气，我相信你会找到钥匙的。

original:
The ventilation system has been checked and the required security and medical protocols have been initiated as per instruction in preparation for release of the Control:  

The following systems have been brought online:
V-Shaft 00209
V-Shaft 00437
V-Shaft 00518
V-Shaft 00518-C

The following systems have been disconnected:
V-Shaft 00014 A-D
V-Shaft 00083 A-D

The following security precautions have also been completed:
Security Protocol 51:46-A
Camera Protocol 52:Overseer
Medical Protocol 98:MedAlert

I have overseen all preliminary tests and can assuredly say we are ready and prepared for the worst.

In the event of my death, the Backup Overseer will oversee the experiments as they continue, and send updates to Vault-Tec.
translation:
通风系统检查完毕，安保医疗协议按照准备释放控制的指令初始化完毕： 

下列系统连线完毕：
V-Shaft 00209
V-Shaft 00437
V-Shaft 00518
V-Shaft 00518-C

下列系统断开连接：
V-Shaft 00014 A-D
V-Shaft 00083 A-D

下列保全系统已经完成：
安保协议 51:46-A
监视协议 52:监督者
医疗协议 98:MedAlert

我监督了所有的初步测试，可以肯定地说，我们准备好了对付最坏的情况。

一旦我遭遇不幸，备用监督者将接替我的职责，继续监督实验，并向避难所科技发送最新进展。

original: We just got these new Hazardous Welding Helmets in from HQ. These things are supposed to keep y'all safer on the line, and improve efficiency while welding. There's an integrated visor that highlights areas of interest. Under no circumstances should these helmets be worn during off hours, or taken outside of the building.\n\nThere's only four of them, so they're going to be given to the best performing workers on each shift. If any of them are damaged or go missing, we may not get a second shipment, people! If anyone sees another worker misusing these helmets, report it to management immediately.
translation:
我们刚从总部收到了这些新款危险焊接头盔。
这些头盔旨在让你们在生产线上更加安全，并提高焊接效率。
它们配备了一个集成护目镜，可以突出显示感兴趣的区域。
在任何情况下，都不应在非工作时间佩戴这些头盔，
也不得将其带出大楼。

我们只有四个这样的头盔，
因此它们将颁发给每个班次表现最好的工人。
如果有人损坏或丢失了头盔，我们可能无法获得第二批货物，
各位！如果有人看到其他工人滥用这些头盔，
请立即向管理层报告。

original: So the pumps are working, and some of the doors are opened. We're making progress.
translation: 水泵工作了，一些门也打开了。我们进展不错。

original: Problem is that the water shorted out a few key fuse boxes. Here, take these fuses and replace the ones that have burnt out.
translation: 问题在于水让一些关键的保险丝盒短路了。给，拿这些保险丝去把烧掉的换掉。

original: So, whatever happened to your father?
translation: 你父亲究竟发生了什么？

original: Oh... oh my god! That's his voice! It's really him!
translation: 哦...天啊，是他的声音，真的是他！

original: I can't believe you brought this to me. I don't know what to say but thank you.
translation: 我不敢相信你给我带来了这，我不知道说什么好，但谢谢你。

original: Wait! Here, take my 10mm Ultra SMG. It's never let me down. Besides, I won't really need it anymore.
translation: 等等！拿上这把10mm“超级”冲锋枪。它从没让我失望过。而且，我不再需要它了。

original: Sydney, I found a note from your father. He didn't abandon you.
translation: 希德妮，我拿到了你父亲的记录，他没有离弃你。

original: Not too heavy, not too light, you find that medium armors fit you just right! While wearing medium armor, your Health and AP are increased by 40, your enemies have -25% crit. chance, and your AP cost with ranged weapons is reduced by 20%.
translation:
不轻不重，你发现中甲非常适合你！
在穿着中等护甲时，你的生命值和行动点数增加40，
你的敌人暴击几率降低25%，
并且你使用远程武器的行动点数消耗减少20%。

original: Yours is a heavy burden, and you need the heaviest of armors to survive it. While in non-powered heavy armor, you gain +25% carry weight, +1 Endurance, +10% combat movement speed, and +15% Unarmed and Melee Weapon damage.
translation:
你肩负着重担，需要最重的护甲来生存。
在穿着重型非动力护甲时，你获得+25%的负重能力，
+1耐力，+10%的战斗移动速度，
以及+15%的徒手和近战武器伤害。

original: Fashion clearly didn't hit its peak until *after* the war. When wearing raider armor, you gain +2 Endurance, +1 Strength, +25 AP, and your Unarmed and Melee Weapon AP cost is reduced by 15%.
translation:
时尚显然在战争之后才达到巅峰。
当你穿着掠夺者护甲时，
你会获得+2耐力，+1力量，+25行动点数，
并且你的徒手和近战武器行动点数消耗减少15%。

original: Since the time of Erasmus, people have known that dressing sharply is the key to success! While wearing clothing, you gain +10% XP, +7 to Barter, Speech, and Sneak, and suffer -50% limb damage.
translation:
自伊拉斯谟时代起，人们便知道，穿着得体是成功的关键！
在穿着衣物时，
你获得+10%的经验值，+7的砍价、口才和潜行技能，
并减少50%的肢体伤害。

original:
You have gained the specialized training needed to move in Power Armor.
Power armor is very protective and durable, but it has both strengths and drawbacks.
It grants +10%% Unarmed and Melee Weapon damage, -50%% spread penalty for moving while aiming, and various stat bonuses.
However, it reduces Unarmed and Melee Weapon attack speed by 15%%, reload speed with non-heavy weapons by 10%%, equip speed by 20%%, and running while sneaking will always incur a detection penalty.
translation:
你已获得装备动力装甲所需的专业训练。
动力装甲非常具有保护性和耐用性，但它既有优点也有缺点。
它提供+10%的徒手和近战武器伤害，
+50%的瞄准移动时的散布惩罚减免，以及各种属性加成。
然而，它会使徒手和近战武器的攻击速度降低15%，
非重型武器的装填速度降低10%，
装备速度降低20%，并且在潜行时奔跑总是会引发检测惩罚。
剩余%.2f秒的视觉充电时间。
